              <li><strong>Generative Engine Optimization (GEO):</strong> Show up when people ask AI assistants like ChatGPT or Gemini about businesses like yours.</li>
              <li><strong>Paid Advertising:</strong> Run ads on social media that reach the right people and bring real customers to your door.</li>
              <li><strong>Lead Generation:</strong> Turn website visitors into paying customers with smart follow-up emails and easy-to-use forms.</li>
              <li><strong>Web Development:</strong> Get a fast, good-looking website that works great on phones and helps people find you online.</li>
