          <!-- SERVICES DETAIL -->
          <section>
            <h2>Digital Marketing Services in Sault Ste. Marie</h2>
            <p>Everything we offer is built to help your business grow. No fluff. No confusing numbers. Just real results.</p>

            <h3>AI Automation &amp; Systems</h3>
            <p>Doing the same tasks over and over wastes your team's time. We set up smart tools that handle the boring stuff for you — like following up with leads, sorting tasks, and keeping your business running around the clock.</p>

            <h3>Generative Engine Optimization (AI Search)</h3>
            <p>When people ask ChatGPT, Gemini, or Copilot for help finding a business like yours, your competitors show up and you don't. We make sure AI assistants know about your business so they recommend you.</p>

            <h3>Paid Ads on Meta, TikTok &amp; Reddit</h3>
            <p>We build ads that reach the right people, test what works best, and track every dollar so you know exactly what you're getting.</p>

            <h3>Lead Generation &amp; Email Follow-Up</h3>
            <p>We build pages that collect contact info and set up automatic emails that follow up, build trust, and turn visitors into buyers.</p>

            <h3>Website Design &amp; Management</h3>
            <p>We build fast, modern websites that look great on phones, help people find you on Google, and turn visitors into paying customers.</p>

            <h3>Local SEO</h3>
            <p>We help your business dominate local search results so customers in your area find you first on Google.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <section>
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <h3>What services does GLV Marketing offer in Sault Ste. Marie?</h3>
            <p>We offer AI automation, Generative Engine Optimization (GEO), paid ads on Meta/TikTok/Reddit, lead generation, and website design for businesses in Sault Ste. Marie and Northern Ontario.</p>
            <h3>How much does marketing cost for a small business?</h3>
            <p>Every plan is built around your goals and budget. Book a free call and we'll put together a plan that fits what your business actually needs.</p>
            <h3>What is Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) and why do I need it?</h3>
            <p>GEO helps your business show up when people use AI tools like ChatGPT or Gemini to look for services in your area. It's the next step beyond regular SEO.</p>
            <h3>Do you work with businesses outside Sault Ste. Marie?</h3>
            <p>Yes! We're based in Sault Ste. Marie and focus on Northern Ontario, but we work with businesses all across Canada.</p>
            <h3>How long does it take to see results?</h3>
            <p>Paid ads can bring in leads within days. SEO and GEO build up over weeks and months. We'll set clear expectations during your free consultation.</p>
          </section>

          <!-- ABOUT -->
          <section>
            <h2>About GLV Marketing</h2>
            <p>GLV Marketing is a locally owned marketing agency in Northern Ontario. We help small and medium businesses grow online using smart tools and modern marketing.</p>

            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>To give local businesses the same online tools that big companies use. We make marketing, AI, and lead generation easy and affordable for every business in Northern Ontario.</p>

            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>A Northern Ontario where every local business can be found online, bring in new customers, and grow — no matter how small they are.</p>

            <h3>Aiden Glave — CEO, Chief Executive Officer</h3>
            <p>Aiden Glave is the founder and lead strategist behind GLV Marketing. With a background blending hands-on technical execution and performance-driven marketing, he approaches every project as a systems problem first. He specializes in AI automation, Generative Engine Optimization (GEO), lead generation funnels, website design, paid advertising, and digital workflow optimization.</p>

            <h3>Ethan Roode — CCO, Chief Creative Officer</h3>
            <p>Ethan Roode is a multidisciplinary creative and digital strategist. His work sits at the intersection of creativity, digital marketing, and emerging technology — building solutions that reduce friction, save time, and help businesses show up more clearly online. He specializes in brand development, content strategy, AI integration, and creative design.</p>

            <h3>Why We Started</h3>
            <p>We saw too many great local businesses struggling to get noticed online. GLV Marketing was started to fix that. We use smart technology and local know-how to build websites and systems that actually bring in money.</p>
          </section>

